title: DAY 7 Back to Basics - 15 MIN FULL BODY STRETCH For Rest Day, Improve Mobility & Flexibility
description:
Day 7 / 14-Day BACK TO BASICS CHALLENGE - Recover on your rest day with this 15 min Full Body Stretch. Take it slow for your body and mind so you're feeling fresh and recharged - ready for another new week of workouts! Enjoy every second of it Team!

♡ SPECIAL YOUTUBE CHALLENGE OFFER: Sign Up for a 1 Month Free Trial for my GROW WITH ANNA APP: https://growwithanna.com/pages/youtube ♡ 

▸ Focus: Recovery & Mobility
▸ Time: 15 Min
▸ Equipment: No Equipment
▸ Workout: 50 sec on, 10 sec off to change to the next stretch ♡ 

Please remember that we are all different and that you can make this your own workout ♡ Take a longer break when you need to.

comments: Team, we’ve made it half way DAY 7 of 14 💪🏼 Give your body this stretch to recover and get ready for new workouts coming next week woohoo #teamgrow ❤❤❤

I’m a 44 year old 6’1” 277lbs. male. I started stretching first thing every morning  about 3 weeks ago. I’ve used other videos until I found this one. I appreciate that there’s no dialog to tire of. I like the transition beeps, along with the image of what’s next and the time to get into position. I find it adequately challenging. I feel refreshed and ready for the day. Excellent video highly recommend!
This is my absolute favorite stretch routine on the whole planet. After doing it I feel refreshed and my body is relieved.
Slow rest days are just as important as the workouts. That’s when our muscles grow 💪🏼

The auditory cues are a blessing. Tells me when i change stretches but also leave me enough time to look at what is next and see how she does it. The song choice is pop but calm ans perfect ans not too loud.
